# Image Proxy Configuration

# For local development (backend running on localhost):
# Create a .env.development file with:
# VITE_IMAGE_PROXY_URL=http://localhost:5000/proxy/image

# For production (after deploying backend to Render):
# DO NOT commit .env.production to GitHub!
# Instead, set this in Vercel dashboard:
# Environment Variable: VITE_IMAGE_PROXY_URL
# Value: https://anigrid-api.onrender.com/proxy/image